👧BLOSSOM: When Raymond and I first met in 2014, we were 17 & 16 years old respectively. 
It was my first Night class at Old Medical Block in school. I remember thinking he was cute 🥰 
We quickly became friends, separated 3years later and got back together in 2021. 
Ours is a 9year old story filled with so many memories, highs and lows. 
However one thing that stayed constant was his love for me (and mine for him, though I fell back in love with him in 2021🌚).
I had no hesitations when I said yes to be with him forever on the 3rd of December 2022🙈
I can safely say that I am getting married to the ONE!
